---
title: Caprese-Inspired Sausage and Flatbreads with Fresh Salad
description: We've taken the classic Capri combo and given it a new twist! With a mix of marinated tomatoes, Italian sausage and creamy bocconcini, this dish is truly freshness in flatbread form!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1016_W31_CA_RV153357-14_Main_low-760c56cf.jpg
